\v 8 X…Ыsib…Фn x…Ы…Ыne bata kala, 
\q1 alo Sibima manpa binle.\f + \fr 16.8 \ft Wudi binla nde na yi, m…Ыn kaane naxanye sima, e yi naxanye bogi yit…Фnma alo manpana e gbee kiini.\f* 
